    15→    /// <summary>
    16→    /// ModelServingSubject is the central hub for runtime-serving events flowing
    17→    /// out of the CanvasCraft inference gallery.  Any component interested in
    18→    /// live prediction metrics, drift reports, or serving-side exceptions can
    19→    /// subscribe to this subject and react in near real-time.
