    21→    /// Design notes:
    22→    /// • Implements IObservable to conform to the Observer pattern.
    23→    /// • Uses a thread-safe collection to keep subscriptions lightweight and lock-free.
    24→    /// • Each event dispatch is fire-and-forget to avoid blocking the inference
    25→    ///   pipeline; back-pressure or throttling is handled upstream by the
    26→    ///   MonitoringPipeline in case of observer overload.
    27→    /// </summary>
